  "description": "The image depicts a large, white, Art Deco-style building situated on a pier extending into calm, blue water. The building has a complex, geometric facade with multiple levels, towers, and a flat roof with visible mechanical equipment. A portion of the building on the left is constructed of corrugated metal. Adjacent to the building, on the pier, are rows of colorful, carnival-like game booths or stalls, adding a playful contrast to the architecture. The background features a lush green hillside. The water is slightly choppy, reflecting the daylight. The overall scene suggests a waterfront entertainment or recreational area.",
